      • loginStudent

        boolean loginStudent(java.lang.String username,
                   java.lang.String password)
        loginStudent takes two parameters representing the username and password of a student. The method will return true if the student with the specified username exists and the given password is correct.
        Parameters:
        username - String representing username of user
        password - String representing password of same user
        Returns:
        True if username exists and password matches, false otherwise.
